high_descs: Turn left and walk over to face the sink.
Pick up the grey glass sitting between the egg and the faucet.
Turn right for one step then left to face the counter.
Place the glass on the counter top, to the bottom left of the lettuce.
Turn left and take one step, turn right and face the sink.
Open the bottom right cabinet under the sink; pick up the grey glass in the cabinet and close the door.
Turn right for one step then left to face the counter.
Set the glass down on the counter top behind the existing glass; close to the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put two grey glasses on the counter next to the lettuce.

high_descs: turn to face the kitchen sink
pick up the glass next to the faucet on the sink edge
walk slightly right to face the counter to the right of the sink
put the glass on the counter to the right of the sink
walk left to face the cabinet below the sink
open the right cabinet door below the sink, pick up the glass inside the cabinet, close the door
walk slightly right to face the counter to the right of the sink
put the glass on the counter to the right of the sink above the other glass
anns.task_desc: put two glasses on a counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the glass, to the right of the faucet, on the back of the sink.
Move over to the counter top to the right of the sink.
Set the glass down near the edge of the counter, to the right of the sink.
Move back over to your left so that you are in front of the sink again.
Pull out a glass from the right cabinet, underneath the sink.
Move back over to the counter top, to the right of the sink.
Place the glass on the counter, behind the other one previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Put two glasses on the counter.
